Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:06.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello, starting today I'll serve as your{\i0}\N{\i1}emcee. I am a French-born Simoun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:11.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, who{\i0}\N{\i1}are you, anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:12.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emcee: Simoun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's guests, please call{\i0}\N{\i1}out the title of this show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Monthly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,ADR!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:23.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bulletin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:27.22,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monthly! ADR Bulletin Special{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:30.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm Mamiko Noto,\Nand I play Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:30.26,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rimone: Mamiko Noto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:34.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Yukana,\Nand I play Domin_u_ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:34.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Domin_u_ra: Yukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:36.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Monthly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:39.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the third time you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:47.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the two of us are\Nin charge of this installment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:51.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,It'll be very calm and gentle,\Na laid-back show...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Calm? I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:56.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Laid-back? Calm and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:58.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:01.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we're just going to be ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:04.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll present\Nthe show in this fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:07.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,We hope you enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:13.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now then, let's start with this corner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:16.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you\Npresenting the show, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,No-holds-barred!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:19.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Brutal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:22.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Live Talk Show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:25.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No-Holds-Barred!?{\i0}\N{\i1}A Brutal, Live Talk Show{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:31.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that's really laid-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Super laid-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:35.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Extremely laid-back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But they must've known\Nwhen they chose us...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:42.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think so? I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:46.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of the whole Simoun cast,\Nwe're the most laid-back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:49.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think so too, Yukana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:54.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please tell us what you've\Nfallen in love with recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:02:01.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please tell us what you've{\i0}\N{\i1}fallen in love with recently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:57.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we've fallen\Nin love with recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vegetable juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vegetable juice is your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:05.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:05.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The sweet kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's kale-based.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:11.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's easier for me to drink if it's\Nkale-based. It's not very sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:15.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's not very bitter,\Nand it tastes very green.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:16.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so in love with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:22.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for me, I was\Ndrinking some just now... Cassis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:25.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean in that little can?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:31.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,People who aren't\Nused to it say it tastes sour...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:35.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it's that sweet\Nand tangy taste that I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:40.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't really see it in stores...\NI mean I've never seen it in stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:45.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Not that\Nmany places carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:49.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on, aren't you two{\i0}\N{\i1}digressing from the subject?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:53.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, then this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:59.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,If there was a Ri M_a_jon you'd like\Nto invent, what would you name it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:04.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there was a Ri M_a_jon you'd like{\i0}\N{\i1}to invent, what would you name it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,A name for a Ri M_a_jon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,How about after a flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, how lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:10.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sounds kinda good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:15.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you flourish it like this... When you\Ndo that, everyone starts smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,l-It's okay. It's okay. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:23.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's keeping with the image\Nof Ri M_a_jons, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Flowers and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:38.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, you!{\i0}\N{\i1}Move this show along, will you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why Oh Why? Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why Oh Why!? Simoun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, now it's time for a quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:54.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun-sama,\Nplease read out the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:04:00.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what is "Tempus Spatium"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:04:00.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what is "Tempus Spatium"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't talk at the same time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,The wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,The deity they worship or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,But how should we explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:21.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our nation,\NSimulacrum Kyuukoku's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Domin_u_ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, h-how should I put it?\NOur one and only... absolute god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, of course{\i0}\N{\i1}she'd get that one right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:41.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is Tempus Spatium?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:41.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,The god worshipped by\Nthe people of Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:45.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium's court protects\Nthe "Spring," its religious center...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:50.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...which is served across\Nthe nation by the great temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:53.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, then that means that the Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:58.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Onasia's spring, the one Elly\Nentered, is the center of their religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now then, time for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Product Presentation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, why'd the camera move?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:12.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, here's what you've been\Nwaiting for, Simoun DVD volume one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:15.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,August 25th, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the date\Nit's going to be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:25.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,And here are the bonus features for\Nthe limited edition. These two here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Postcards by the character designer,\NNishida-san, will be included.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:36.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,And this time around,\Nthe pairing is of Neviril and Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:42.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun DVD volume 1\Nwill be released on August 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:45.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,We hope you'll support Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some closing words please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:54.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You could've just spoken{\i0}\N{\i1}in Japanese from the start...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:58.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right... That's about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, we've come to the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,That went by really fast, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,How was it, Mamiko Noto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:13.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it felt as though time\Nwas passing very, very slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:19.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it was great getting the chance\Nto talk to you like this one-on-one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:22.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...because although\Nwe do chat during breaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:28.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was the first time we did\Na presentation and discussed Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:32.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, it was a valuable opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:37.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I... Normally, when\NI'm talking with Mamiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't really say a lot, unlike today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:45.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling some people\Nwill be like, "You talk even {\i1}less?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Words aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:50.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's not\Na matter of words, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Usually, I'll just look at her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:57.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and maybe say\Nsomething once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:02.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,So for the two of us,\NI think we talked a {\i1}lot{\i0} today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really hope you all enjoyed our chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:09.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that ends our\NMonthly ADR Bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:17.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't miss the next episode!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good night... Good night...
